  "content": "<h1>Paths</h1>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #15171a;\">Everything on a path is automatically transferred to the character sheet. You as a player only need to mark which attributes you want to increase. An exception is paths like the Rogue where you need to make a choice regarding Roguery Talents. You have to select the one you want and click the transfer button to add it to your character sheet.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #15171a;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #15171a;\">Figure 1: A path in view mode</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/mJBdQDn/Screenshot-2021-02-19-at-14-38-11.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"429\" height=\"740\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #15171a;\">Figure 2: A path in edit mode<br /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/GTSP5vm/Screenshot-2021-02-19-at-14-38-33.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"429\" height=\"579\" /><br /><br /></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; color: #191813; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">The sheet consists of the following fields:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\n<li class=\"li2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">An Image<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" /></li>\n<li class=\"li2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Name of the Talent<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" /></li>\n<li class=\"li2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Below the name is a label that tells you that Item type this is.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Path Type: Novice, Expert or Master<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #131310;\">A list of levels. Each level look like the one in figure 2. There is a button to the right that allows you to add a level to a path.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #131310;\">Level: Enter what level this is.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #10100e;\">Attributes: Choose what type of attribute advancement you need for this path.<br />Enter the value you gain by selecting the attributes.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #131310;\">Characteristics: The level bonus on each characteristics.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #131310;\">Languages and Professions: Write whatever the Core Rules are saying.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #10100e;\">Equipment: Some SotDL supplements&nbsp;grants you some starting equipment.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #10100e;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">Magic: Just write that the Core Rules are saying.<br /><br /></span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #0e0e0d;\">Talents: The dotted lines are a drop zone and when you drag/drop a talent on it it&rsquo;s stored on the path.</li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #0e0e0d;\">Talents (choose one): Works the way talents does.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #0e0e0d;\">Spells: Works the same way as talents does except it's spells you add.</li>\n</ul>",
